{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cadcccf258","title":"新“九品”释","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"77b9f3f004","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"cadcccf258"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"860082c4c6","name":"朱承立"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bd05ab6460","type":"title","text":"新“九品”释","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"b01412bcf7","type":"authors","text":"北京大学朱承立","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"1ac9a83621","type":"subtitle","text":"（朱承立：北京大学西语系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"975240500e","type":"paragraph","text":"昔两晋设“九品中正”门阀制度，因此产生，今西语系三年级有新“九品”，“九品”之间有不可逾越之鸿沟，彼此不通思想，甚至不通语言。特列表说明如下：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"2840d432f2","type":"paragraph","text":"党员：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"1ac52e34a1","type":"paragraph","text":"元老党员          永远正确，小事不管，大事一句“金言”幕后决定一切。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"c3218faf6e","type":"paragraph","text":"当权派党员        道貌岸然荣誉永属自己，错误永属别人，群众和落后团员。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"60300df651","type":"paragraph","text":"新入和预备党员    小心翼翼，由群众中来，但不到群众中去。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"701455a7d8","type":"paragraph","text":"党培养对象的团员  以唯唯诺诺歌功颂德，吹吹拍拍，以小汇报甚至打击别人为入党之阶。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"4e8f40b66e","type":"paragraph","text":"团员：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"9945113207","type":"paragraph","text":"一般团员          沉默寡言，只知举手赞成，跟着说，跟着走，有不平亦不敢提。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"0969ad7e29","type":"paragraph","text":"“落后”团员      爱提反面意见不但被视为落后，而且与组织对立。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"bcb10c4cef","type":"paragraph","text":"群众：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"1a66b79f13","type":"paragraph","text":"团培养对象的群众　看准风头，一味吹捧。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"31c1cd4b8c","type":"paragraph","text":"一般群众          对入团心灰意懒，埋头于图书，寄惦于音乐。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"4655b79e07","type":"paragraph","text":"“落后”群众      其中有被除的团员，肃反被斗错的，他们永被摒弃于千里之外，无人过问。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"},{"id":"160ef83e06","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《校内外右派言论汇集》(北京大学经济系政治经济学教研室，1957年8月）。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258"}],"page":{"id":"5b30228990","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cadcccf258","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}